subject: pcie_bifurcation: Fetch highest level bifurcation at a PCIe slot
commitMessage:
pcie_bifurcation: Fetch highest level bifurcation at a PCIe slot

Use the new FruDevice Decorator `Bifurcation` to fetch the bifurcation
at each device.

Tested:
Unit tests passed.

Physical Tests.

PE0 -> no bifurcation
PE1 -> x8x8

```
$ ipmitool raw 0x2e 0x32 0x79 0x2b 0x00 0x0b 0
 79 2b 00 0b 00

$ ipmitool raw 0x2e 0x32 0x79 0x2b 0x00 0x0b 1
 79 2b 00 0b 02 08 08
```

Change-Id: Id811897cad82a36da29cd8795f8bc6e855a7e96d
Signed-off-by: Willy Tu <wltu@google.com>
